caption.text:
You have to feel it to believe it. 

NEW Soft Pinch Matte Bouncy Blush launches March 27. 

Choose from 7 pigment-rich shades of this buildable putty-like formula that blends like cream and blurs like powder. 

@lordthivi (she/her) wears Happy

Congratulations to Founder @selenagomez and the Rare Impact Fund for being honored in the @NatGeo 33 — an inaugural list of changemakers whose ideas, influence, and drive are shaping a better future for our planet. 

Photographer: @cassblackbird
Stylist: @jan.quammie
Hair: @renatocampora
Makeup: @raoulalejandre
Nails: @tombachik 

#NatGeo33

Currently on repeat: Sunset Blvd to go with my sunset blush combo.

Pro Artist @rays_beauty__ (she/her) wears Soft Pinch Liquid Blush in Virtue, Happy, and Positive Light Liquid Luminizer in Flaunt.

What’s yours?

And on that note, here’s a #rarereminder Rare Impact Fund mental health partner, Child Mind Institute, to save for yourself or share with a friend:

“Confidence and positive self-image are about more than knowing that you’re good at math or liking the way you look. They depend on being able to bounce back from setbacks and being willing to try new things and fail.”
